{"tid":1187336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來根據警方估計, 維園中央草坪可以容納 32,000 人","createTime":"2019-06-05T14:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T17:10:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b59744f0f34a9934ba0a593011d9c4aae91461","tid":1187336,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"原來根據警方估計, 維園中央草坪可以容納 32,000 人<br />\n<br />\n6個維園硬地足球場比中央草坪更大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61774416_2203767869713595_8382367708871655424_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=e719be66b2becec4b0e6370b3ab3d0b4&amp;oe=5D8CFA45\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61774416_2203767869713595_8382367708871655424_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3De719be66b2becec4b0e6370b3ab3d0b4%26oe%3D5D8CFA45&h=308d3230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果琴晚六四驚方話係 3.7萬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61953384_2203767913046924_167005693021257728_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=901cc8ae222bc101aa7e7d6ca814fe92&amp;oe=5D8D9F25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61953384_2203767913046924_167005693021257728_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D901cc8ae222bc101aa7e7d6ca814fe92%26oe%3D5D8D9F25&h=9ead50c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒 Au Nok-hin<br />\n6小時 &middot; <br />\n【差佬數人數的荒謬性】<br />\n<br />\n尋晚警方數到六四晚會得37,000人，心諗&hellip;你講曬啦。<br />\n<br />\n正正係以前做民陣召集人，令我對差佬奇妙的數人數方法有更深入認識。下圖係我地籌辦遊行時警方說服民陣用維園草地的估算，佢聲稱草地裝到32,000人。加埋銅鑼灣同天后幾條街，一共裝到62,250人。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚集會開始無耐去左草地，全部爆晒之餘，市民已經開始進佔成條緩跑徑同音樂亭走廊，到九點為止一路有人係天后同銅鑼灣入黎，點解又會得出37,000人呢？<br />\n<br />\n我連六個足球場你計幾多都未算帳。係咪撐警集會、反佔中集會你就計多D，你唔喜歡就求其作個數？(註)<br />\n<br />\n你無野呀？ 香港警察 Hong Kong Police?<br />\n<br />\n來源：2017年民陣與警方商討七一遊行的會議<br />\n註： 政情網上行<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.276896536496&hellip;/414974182688451/&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fa.276896536496%E2%80%A6%2F414974182688451%2F%E2%80%A6&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=fc522063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.276896536496&hellip;/414974182688451/&hellip;</a><br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/nokhinau/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fnokhinau%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=3a5e8771\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/nokhinau/posts/?ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"0c24f07970acccce34bf1f4f82e00a0627727929","tid":1187336,"uid":148332,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"講個笑話:警方係政治中立既"},{"pid":"d35415a5ed7059939dcaddee8091ae5d06b4e58f","tid":1187336,"uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0c24f07970acccce34bf1f4f82e00a0627727929","tid":1187336,"uid":148332,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"講個笑話:警方係政治中立既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"搵返幾年前嗰D 乜嘢愛國集會. 幾百人都冇. 差佬話有幾萬人. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac8cb0ac8e6ddc48b2e5e97b5c49e5e5f84eb3b","tid":1187336,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"自己計下"},{"pid":"6e0f24b384f727cd0fbcf979908f8f1009c55985","tid":1187336,"uid":69215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"毅進仔數手指都未撚數得掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  體諒下啦 人地數學U架"},{"pid":"a6a795c60e0a12bd084221ece5a